Name: The Quikscell Company
Details: The Quikscell Company is known as the Quicksell Company, Quickscell Company, Quicsell Company, and many other variations, changing names frequently to avoid lawsuits and weasel out of small print. While an immediately recognisable name throughout the Inner Sphere, it is not for good reasons - Quikscell goods are notoriously low quality and are mass produced to flood the market.
